程序包 jep.python

类 PyPointer

java.lang.Object
java.lang.ref.Reference<T>
java.lang.ref.WeakReference<PyObject>
jep.python.PyPointer
public class PyPointer extends WeakReference<PyObject>
Contains pointers to a JepThread* and a PyObject* for using a PyObject* in Java as a PyObject or its subclasses.
从以下版本开始:
3.8
作者:
Nate Jensen

    • PyPointer

      protected PyPointer(PyObject referrent, MemoryManager memoryManager, long pyObject) throws JepException
      Constructor
      参数:
      referrent - the PyObject (or subclass) corresponding to this PyPointer
      memoryManager - the MemoryManager responsible for tracking this pointer
      pyObject - the pointer to the PyObject*
      抛出:
      JepException - if an error occurs

  • 方法详细资料

    • dispose

      protected void dispose() throws JepException
      Decrefs the PyObject* associated with this PyPointer. When a Python object reaches zero references, it is available for Python garbage collection.
      抛出:
      JepException - if an error occurs
